<section class="section-block" data-section-type="network">
	<h2>Network model</h2>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>Carrier handoffs</strong> — Describe redundant carrier handoffs per POP only where current network inventory confirms them.</li>
		<li><strong>Failover</strong> — Explain routing failover at a platform level and keep service-specific guarantees in agreements.</li>
		<li><strong>Availability target</strong> — Use 99.99% as a voice availability target, not a universal SLA, unless signed terms say otherwise.</li>
		<li><strong>Status history</strong> — Publish incident summaries and monthly uptime only when the status feed is connected.</li>
	</ul>
</section>

